  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Chinoike Clan</p><p>To improve your manipulation of blood, you decide to take some time to study in the medical industry. You gain the following benefits;</p><p>• You gain the ability to learn jutsu with the Medical keyword.</p><p>• All Chinoike Clan Hijutsu you know gain the Medical keyword</p><p>• Medical jutsu you cast can benefit from your Sanguine Prowess feature and Ketsuryūgan bonus action ability</p><p>• Twice per long rest, when you heal a creature with a jutsu with the medical keyword, you can automatically remove all ranks of bleeding from them.</p>",
